headline: Waste Management (NYSE:WM) Misses Q1 Revenue Estimates
summary: Waste management services provider Waste Management (NYSE:WM) fell short of the market’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2025, but sales rose 16.7% year on year to $6.02 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.67 per share was 5.2% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
